(1922, 13467, '出走 EXODUS', '把我的雙手綁起 我要寫越多的歌\r\nIf you tie my hands up, I’ll write more songs\r\n把我的嘴塞起 我要唱到越大聲\r\nIf you stuff my mouth up, I’ll sing even louder\r\n把我的目睭摀起 越黑我越不驚\r\nIf you cover my eyes, I won’t be scared of the dark\r\n把我的頭剁起 你得不到我的生命\r\nIf you cut my head off, you still won’t have my life \r\n\r\n', '2009-06-03 00:00:00', 0, 1, 2, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2009-06-03 01:04:27', '2015-02-16 15:47:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
